12/11/2004
ANKARA, Turkey -- Prime Minister Recep Tayyip Erdogan is attending the Cairo funeral of Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat, the government said in a statement released Thursday (11 November).
Foreign Minister Abdullah Gul is accompanying Erdogan.
In other news, the foreign relations committee in the Turkish Parliament has adopted a resolution declaring that terrorism will not be treated as a political crime.
The draft measure must still be adopted by the full parliament.
(Anadolu Agency, NTV - 11/11/04)
